snippet.title: Ark of The Kosmoz: Initial Trailer
snippet.description:
Ark of The Kosmoz is an arcade top-down shooter that lets you command an army of starships to fight against the force of void! Gather your fleet into formations, and build your team of evolving synergistic compositions. Order your army of Starforce through space and protect the cosmos!

A small game made by small team of solo indie dev, BinaryStella!

STEAM LINK:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2701870/Ark_of_The_Kosmoz/

ITCH.IO:
https://binarystella.itch.io/ark-of-the-kosmoz
